Introduction

Min is a Thai singer and actor under APLAN INTERNATIONAL. He is best known for participating in the reality survival shows Under Nineteen and Boys Planet.

On May 24, 2023, Min announced that he, Haruto, Anthonny, and Minseok had left WAKEONE.
